  "texts": [
    "The conclusion to be drawn from this is that artificial intelligence still needs to be capable of completely replacing humans in the workforce (Vrontis et al., 2021).",
    "The literature review and analysis led the researcher to develop a model for adopting AI infrastructure in the business (Fig. 1).",
    "As the literature review suggests, AI in marketing leads to data and content optimization.",
    "Different audiences can be assessed through data optimization, and personalization becomes easy as AI quickly processes enormous amounts of data.",
    "Efficiency increases, and the content creation becomes more relevant, precise, and personalized."
  ]
}